description:
This is a 18 minute workout called 'Hydrow Games: Training Day with Dani' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Competitor and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Prepare yourself for the ultimate endurance test with Dani in this 16-minute Training Day session. This sweat-packed workout mimics the intensity and structure of a 5,000-meter race. Kick-off with a high rhythm start, followed by powerful strokes to build endurance. Dani guides you with positive self-talk and visualization techniques essential for race day success. Experience max pressure intervals to sharpen your strategy and boost your confidence. Push your limits and get ready to achieve peak performance. Max rhythm: 34. Format: Intervals...
